And I know that you want to live up to that.

35:40.767 --> 35:42.790
And so why don't we, why don't we rein it in a little bit?

35:42.810 --> 35:45.535
And why don't you live up to the potential that you have in life?

35:45.875 --> 35:48.719
And this kid was like, yeah, I'm the man, right?

35:49.000 --> 35:50.041
See that my wife understood.

35:50.061 --> 35:51.664
So I was like, get out of here, you stupid kid.

35:52.125 --> 35:53.106
My wife goes, no, no.

35:53.378 --> 35:56.502
You're a little king, right?

35:57.123 --> 35:58.805
The crowning, you're a little queen.

35:58.886 --> 36:02.731
I wanna pull out of you all of your wonderful, beautiful potential.

36:03.652 --> 36:04.593
This is what I want from you.

36:04.613 --> 36:18.392
And then the whole thing ends as it says, man, God, you've given us as human beings dominion over the works of your hands and you put all things under his feet, all sheep and oxen, the beast, the fields, the birds, the heavens, the fish, the sea, whatever passes along the path of the earth.

36:18.833 --> 36:22.418
And what he's trying to say is you have responsibility right now in this world

36:22.594 --> 36:23.795
to do something amazing.

36:23.835 --> 36:25.878
This is the beautiful part about being a human being.

36:26.378 --> 36:27.700
You've been given a task.

36:27.740 --> 36:29.161
The task is more than your job.

36:29.181 --> 36:30.523
It's more than just raising a family.

36:30.603 --> 36:31.504
It is those things.

36:31.584 --> 36:32.565
It's beautifully those things.

36:32.585 --> 36:35.208
And you're going to be held, but it's to live for the glory of God.

36:35.228 --> 36:36.249
And I'll just end this way.

36:36.930 --> 36:41.856
The book of Hebrews goes on to take a passage like this and say, you know who this passage really was all about?

36:42.116 --> 36:46.321
Of course, this whole idea of human beings are in the center of running the universe, all the sheep and oxen.

36:46.341 --> 36:47.442
They're all under them.

36:48.226 --> 36:51.913
God had this concept that a human being would be in the center of running the universe.

36:52.013 --> 37:04.276
And this ultimately took place in the person of the work of Jesus Christ, the one who is God who became the ultimate human being for you and died on a cross for your sin and rose again for your salvation.

37:04.296 --> 37:09.586
So you could ultimately reign in heaven as kings and queens in a sense.

37:09.794 --> 37:11.216
This is what Jesus Christ has done.

37:11.256 --> 37:13.380
And some of you may be wrestling with that.

37:13.400 --> 37:15.123
Like, I don't know if I've become a Christian.

37:15.383 --> 37:17.106
And this is an opportunity to go, I want to do that.

37:17.206 --> 37:18.989
I want to become a Christian today.

37:19.009 --> 37:20.812
I want to give my life to Jesus today.

37:20.872 --> 37:28.124
And others of you are just going to be in awe of the role that God has for you, the majestic awe of what He's done and what He's called you to do.

37:28.164 --> 37:29.586
So Father, I pray.

37:30.114 --> 37:51.570
that you would give us your grace in this, that we would be an absolute awe of the beautiful world you've created, but how it trickles down, as this writer says, to something about us, the way we live our life, not in anxiety and fear and trying to earn everything, but arresting in you and what you've done, the fact that you made all that and you care for us above it all.

37:52.194 --> 38:05.149
and the task that we have before our lives to walk out of these doors and live for your glory and the good of this world is just something that will wake us up in the morning and give us purpose and steel in our spine and let us trust in you, Jesus.

38:05.209 --> 38:13.518
Those here, maybe we've never given their lives to you, Jesus, that they would accept your gift of salvation for them and their heart and they would live for you, Jesus.

38:13.558 --> 38:20.466
The true human being who came and showed us what it means to be human and we could follow that in all things.

38:20.898 --> 38:22.977
for your glory in Jesus' great name we pray.

38:23.481 --> 38:23.804
Amen.

